(# Core Blueprint — Bottleneck Zero) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Promise) Tj
T*
(Install a 24-hour follow-up engine that reduces response lag, improves lead quality) Tj
T*
(conversations, and increases booked calls/sales from existing inbound leads.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Outcome Targets \(first 14 days\)) Tj
T*
(- Median first-response time: under 10 minutes) Tj
T*
(- % of leads receiving 3+ touches in 72 hours: 80%+) Tj
T*
(- Ghosted lead reactivation reply rate: 10–20% baseline target) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## System Architecture) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Stage 1: First Touch \(0–10 minutes\)) Tj
T*
(Goal: acknowledge context and secure micro-commitment.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Message structure:) Tj
T*
(1. Personal context mirror) Tj
T*
(2. Relevant one-liner value anchor) Tj
T*
(3. Low-friction question) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Stage 2: Qualification + Objection Handling \(10 minutes–24 hours\)) Tj
T*
(Goal: progress conversation with clarity.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Rules:) Tj
T*
(- Never send walls of text) Tj
T*
(- Ask one question at a time) Tj
T*
(- Objections are signals of uncertainty; answer with clarity + proof) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Stage 3: Ghost Revival \(24–72 hours\)) Tj
T*
(Goal: re-open with value, not pressure.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Cadence:) Tj
T*
(- T+24h: fresh insight) Tj
T*
(- T+48h: mini proof/case) Tj
T*
(- T+72h: simple forked close question) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Implementation Workflow) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. Connect lead source \(DM form, website form, calendar no-show list\).) Tj
T*
(2. Tag every new lead with `new_inbound` + timestamp.) Tj
T*
(3. Trigger Script 1 immediately.) Tj
T*
(4. If no reply after 2 hours, send Script 2.) Tj
T*
(5. If reply includes objection, switch to Script 3 or 4.) Tj
T*
(6. If no activity by day 1, trigger ghost revival sequence.) Tj
